硫化氢与高铼酸作用，产生暗棕色的[[七硫化二铼|七硫化二铼]]沉淀：<ref name=fml>《无机化学反应方程式手册》. 曹忠良等主编. P<sub>320</sub>. 【HReO<sub>4</sub>】</ref>
: 2 HReO<sub>4</sub> + 7 H<sub>2</sub>S → Re<sub>2</sub>S<sub>7</sub>↓ + 8 H<sub>2</sub>O

在有机合成上，高铼酸可以催化[[肟|肟]]脱水，转变为[[腈|腈]]：<ref>{{cite journal | author = Ishihara, K.; Furuya, Y.; Yamamoto, H. | title = Rhenium(VII) Oxo Complexes as Extremely Active Catalysts in the Dehydration of Primary Amides and Aldoximes to Nitriles | journal = [[Angewandte_Chemie,_International_Edition|Angewandte Chemie, International Edition]] | volume = 41 | pages = 2983–2986 | year = 2002 | doi = 10.1002/1521-3773(20020816)41:16<2983::AID-ANIE2983>3.0.CO;2-X | issue = 16 }}</ref>

